A Personal Education Dashboard Software - Comet Dash
	1.1 Views
		1.1.1 Landing Page: Overview of stattics: upon click shows more information show all days in a month, and event snippet for each day
		1.1.2 Grade Averages: at a glance grades for classes 
		1.1.3 RMP: stats also add a review show all events in a day, sorted by their starting time
		1.1.4 Syllabus view (optional): show all events in future as a list
		1.1.5 Exam registrations
		1.1.6 Study statistics: times, session, points or streaks system
	1.2 Events
		1.2.1 Add an event with starting and ending time
		1.2.2 Check exam registrations and conflicts
		1.2.3 Add weekly due date times
		1.2.4 
		1.2.5 Event alert (optional)
		1.2.6 Add/delete event categories
		1.2.7 Color marking for different category of events
	1.3 Share (optional)
		1.3.1 Send event to other calendar users (requiring their permission) through internet
	1.4 Other
		1.4.1 Holidays & weekends should be in special colors
		1.4.2 Zoom in/out, and scroll support when necessary